      "message": "I wonder should we use an annotation name that includes some indication in the name that it's a verification annotation. Maybe VerifyKey or VerifyNotNull. It's just when I saw this first i thought the @NotNull one was the Lombok @NonNull annotation.\n\nI guess this would be a change on the policy/common parameters code as well.",
